24
00:02:54,396 --> 00:02:56,197
If so,

25
00:02:56,197 --> 00:02:59,669
why didn't Lingering An sing it with affection?

26
00:03:01,538 --> 00:03:05,869
Did you not sing well because you see His Majesty and I together,

27
00:03:05,869 --> 00:03:08,002
