34
00:03:26,259 --> 00:03:28,081
Her voice was just fine!

35
00:03:28,833 --> 00:03:30,345
Songzhi

36
00:03:30,345 --> 00:03:32,857
Pour Lingering An a cup of sweet rose wine

37
00:03:33,892 --> 00:03:36,565
Fend off the cold, and continue singing

38
00:03:36,565 --> 00:03:37,772
Yes

39
00:03:41,081 --> 00:03:43,838
Niang Niang, when I'm singing,

40
00:03:43,838 --> 00:03:46,147
I can't consume anything too sweet, greasy, or spicy.

41
00:03:47,276 --> 00:03:50,325
You can't sing songs, or drink wine

42
00:03:51,209 --> 00:03:53,631
His Majesty summoned you here

43
00:03:54,554 --> 00:03:57,401
It's fine if you disregard me,

44
00:03:57,401 --> 00:03:58,804
but His Majesty...

45
00:04:01,968 --> 00:04:08,165
Since Princess of Glory granted the wine, just drink it

46
00:04:15,892 --> 00:04:16,834
Yes

47
00:04:36,167 --> 00:04:38,135
Pick a good song to sing

48
00:05:00,688 --> 00:05:02,493
Are you alright?

49
00:05:07,068 --> 00:05:08,570
Your Majesty and Niang Niang,

50
00:05:09,021 --> 00:05:10,944
A song accompanied by music

51
00:05:10,944 --> 00:05:12,481
is definitely the most elegant

52
00:05:13,052 --> 00:05:15,280
But sometimes, a poem accompanied by music

53
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,656
can also be refreshing

54
00:05:18,085 --> 00:05:19,550
May I try?

55
00:05:20,471 --> 00:05:21,462
Yes

56
00:05:24,277 --> 00:05:25,180
Yes

57
