Alright, His Majesty and I are tired

59
00:06:33,583 --> 00:06:34,730
You've worked hard

60
00:06:38,061 --> 00:06:39,233
Zhou Ning Hai

61
00:06:39,233 --> 00:06:39,727
Yes

62
00:06:39,727 --> 00:06:41,567
Escort them out

63
00:06:41,567 --> 00:06:42,782
Yes

64
00:06:44,459 --> 00:06:45,749
We take our leave

65
00:06:46,530 --> 00:06:47,550
Go

66
