78
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:58,025
This jade pendant from her

79
00:07:58,025 --> 00:07:59,600
what a nuisance!

80
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,541
Does she think I'm a singing geisha? Reward?!

81
00:08:01,541 --> 00:08:02,711
Young mistress!

82
00:08:02,711 --> 00:08:04,551
Young mistress, be angry if you must

83
00:08:04,551 --> 00:08:05,771
but if you really break this,

84
00:08:05,771 --> 00:08:07,820
