85
00:08:12,972 --> 00:08:14,221
Don't cry

86
00:08:15,003 --> 00:08:17,469
Your voice is not well

87
00:08:17,469 --> 00:08:19,797
Have some water

88
00:08:19,797 --> 00:08:23,660
Jiejie, I let you be humiliated along with me today

89
00:08:24,886 --> 00:08:27,063
If you hadn't been there today,

90
00:08:27,063 --> 00:08:28,759
the emperor to keep up appearance's sake,

91
00:08:29,509 --> 00:08:32,492
I don't know how much more torment I would have to endure from her.

92
00:08:34,422 --> 00:08:36,950
His Majesty values Nian Gengyao right now

93
00:08:36,950 --> 00:08:38,490
Princess of Glory is very pleased with herself

94
00:08:40,108 --> 00:08:41,871
For the sake of the broader situation,

95
00:08:42,834 --> 00:08:44,302
for us

96
00:08:44,302 --> 00:08:45,572
His Majesty cannot rip her face too much.

97
00:08:45,572 --> 00:08:47,824
I just hope Nian Gengyao leaves soon

98
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:50,115
