99
00:08:51,035 --> 00:08:52,604
It's not that easy

100
00:08:54,321 --> 00:08:56,819
Leaving aside His Majesty's former feelings for Princess of Glory,

101
00:08:57,916 --> 00:09:00,013
as long as Nian Gengyao is around,

102
00:09:00,901 --> 00:09:04,171
His Majesty will not give her the cold shoulder.

103
00:09:06,333 --> 00:09:08,552
As Niang Niang ordered, servant went to the Palace of Wings

104
00:09:09,089 --> 00:09:11,154
Originally I wanted to say Empress was sick in bed,

105
00:09:11,154 --> 00:09:13,465
so you can't attend the chrysanthemum festival tomorrow

106
00:09:13,465 --> 00:09:15,166
Who knew I'd hear Xiao Xiazi say

107
00:09:15,166 --> 00:09:16,648
that Precious Smile and Lingering An

108
00:09:16,648 --> 00:09:18,347
were performing for Princess of Glory's amusement.

109
00:09:18,931 --> 00:09:20,714
I was nosy and stayed around a bit longer

110
00:09:21,222 --> 00:09:23,573
When Precious Smile and Lingering An came out,

111
00:09:23,573 --> 00:09:26,392
they looked normal and nothing much happened

112
00:09:26,392 --> 00:09:29,070
I know Precious Smile's temperament

113
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:30,774
She's not easily irritable

114
00:09:31,552 --> 00:09:35,385
But I never thought that Lingering An would be able to bear it too.

115
00:09:36,322 --> 00:09:39,016
it seems that I have been less observant

116
00:09:39,016 --> 00:09:40,636
That's in public

117
00:09:40,636 --> 00:09:42,760
Who knows what she's like when she returns home

118
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:45,267
If she can bear it, of course that's good

119
00:09:46,303 --> 00:09:48,610
Princess of Glory is overly arrogant and willful

120
00:09:48,610 --> 00:09:50,139
and humilates others at will

121
00:09:50,139 --> 00:09:52,509
In the end, others will humiliate her

122
00:09:53,465 --> 00:09:55,274
But this Lingering An

123
00:09:55,923 --> 00:09:57,298
She's alright

124
00:10:02,975 --> 00:10:04,297
Over here!

125
00:10:05,306 --> 00:10:06,884
I'm over here!

126
00:10:07,596 --> 00:10:09,062
These plum blossoms are the prettiest!

127
00:10:09,062 --> 00:10:10,793
Young mistress be careful!

128
00:10:10,793 --> 00:10:11,588
Can't catch me! Faster!

129
00:10:15,530 --> 00:10:16,162
Faster

130
00:10:16,162 --> 00:10:17,424
Young mistress, be careful!

131
00:10:18,228 --> 00:10:19,593
Can't catch me!

132
00:10:20,177 --> 00:10:21,337
Can't catch me!

133
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:30,272
Young mistress, put on another layer of clothes

134
00:10:31,027 --> 00:10:33,754
it is still snowing. please wear a coat. it will be very cold.

135
00:10:34,754 --> 00:10:38,121
Look

136
00:10:38,121 --> 00:10:40,138
I haven't heard this type of laughter for a while

137
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:51,635
Precious Smile and Lingering An sent over lots of charcoal

138
00:10:51,635 --> 00:10:53,193
Let me burn some for you

139
00:10:58,293 --> 00:11:00,616
Burn or not, that's not important

140
00:11:01,608 --> 00:11:04,897
Even if it warms the body, it can't warm the heart

141
00:11:11,194 --> 00:11:12,431
young mistress returned.

142
00:11:22,252 --> 00:11:25,057
didn't you want to see the flowers in the yard?

143
00:11:25,057 --> 00:11:26,854
why come back so early?

144
00:11:26,854 --> 00:11:28,874
looking at the flowers for too makes me feel dizzy

145
00:11:29,738 --> 00:11:33,063
Dear 4th was kind to have plum blossoms planted in the courtyard

146
00:11:33,063 --> 00:11:35,361
But when it snows, they're all the same color

147
00:11:35,361 --> 00:11:36,554
now all the white flowers and the snow are blended together

148
00:11:37,665 --> 00:11:38,936
That's easy

149
00:11:40,027 --> 00:11:41,665
if you like the red ones,

150
00:11:42,356 --> 00:11:45,467
I'll let the servants,

151
00:11:45,467 --> 00:11:46,761
bring them all to your palace.

152
00:11:48,916 --> 00:11:51,459
Didn't you want me to concentrate on writing?

153
00:11:51,459 --> 00:11:53,782
How come now you are throwing off my concentration by talking about these things?

154
00:11:53,782 --> 00:11:55,535
Shameless

155
00:11:55,535 --> 00:11:57,644
You're the one who's not concentrating, but you blame others

156
00:11:58,254 --> 00:12:00,944
If I hadn't just lost three rounds of chess to you,

157
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:03,900
I wouldn't be enduring this punishment right now.

158
00:12:03,900 --> 00:12:05,314
Dear 4th's words carry weight

159
00:12:05,766 --> 00:12:08,469
You can't go back on your word

160
00:12:08,469 --> 00:12:09,613
Alright

161
00:12:10,289 --> 00:12:11,883
Huan Huan is also

162
00:12:11,883 --> 00:12:13,618
making a coat for Dear 4th as a gift.

163
00:12:15,878 --> 00:12:18,358
It's fine if I go back on my words.

164
00:12:18,358 --> 00:12:21,816
Simply because you thought of personally making a coat for me,

165
00:12:21,816 --> 00:12:24,878
I would copy three times and not mind.

166
00:12:24,878 --> 00:12:27,288
Dear 4th said it yourself!

167
00:12:27,288 --> 00:12:30,959
To copy all the song lyrics about plum blossoms for Huan Huan

168
00:12:30,959 --> 00:12:32,253
Don't renege!

169
00:12:37,635 --> 00:12:40,233
You applied clear paper onto the windows

170
00:12:40,233 --> 00:12:42,224
The color of snow pours in from outside

171
00:12:42,224 --> 00:12:44,155
It's even brighter than Hall of Resting Soul

172
00:12:45,131 --> 00:12:47,952
I don't like the room to be dark

173
00:12:47,952 --> 00:12:51,183
Besides, once it rains or snows, we use up a lot of candles

174
00:12:51,183 --> 00:12:54,025
Not only does the air smell, it's also too wasteful

175
00:12:54,025 --> 00:12:55,574
You are quite frugal

176
00:12:56,604 --> 00:12:58,954
Not to mention other expenses,

177
00:12:58,954 --> 00:13:02,504
the candle expenses in the inner palace have increased considerably.

178
00:13:02,504 --> 00:13:04,291
Although it's not a huge number,

179
00:13:04,836 --> 00:13:07,065
it is still an expense.

180
00:13:07,065 --> 00:13:08,773
I'm stingy,

181
00:13:08,773 --> 00:13:10,443
it's very kind of Your Majesty to still like me

182
00:13:11,132 --> 00:13:12,670
When I see the Empress,

183
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:14,789
I also want to tell her this idea.

184
00:13:16,319 --> 00:13:19,666
Cut costs in the inner palace wherever possible

185
00:13:21,061 --> 00:13:22,864
It's almost the end of the year

186
00:13:22,864 --> 00:13:24,943
If some money could be saved to create a rice factory

187
00:13:24,943 --> 00:13:27,351
and give aid to the people, it would be good charity.

188
00:13:27,911 --> 00:13:29,896
Then I'll tell the Empress to do it

189
00:13:34,552 --> 00:13:35,998
Auspicious greetings to young mistress Chun

190
00:13:35,998 --> 00:13:36,689
Where's Wan Jiejie?

191
00:13:36,689 --> 00:13:37,673
Inside

192
00:13:38,748 --> 00:13:40,256
Young mistress, the Emperor is also inside

193
00:13:40,256 --> 00:13:40,856
Young mistress!

194
00:13:44,042 --> 00:13:46,211
Wan Jiejie!

195
00:13:46,211 --> 00:13:47,423
Chun'er is here?

196
00:13:47,423 --> 00:13:48,530
Auspicious greetings, Your Majesty

197
00:13:49,089 --> 00:13:50,148
Jiejie, look

198
00:13:50,148 --> 00:13:52,344
Aren't the plum blossoms Chun'er picked for you pretty?

199
00:13:52,344 --> 00:13:53,204
Yes they're pretty

200
00:13:53,204 --> 00:13:54,963
It's so warm here

201
00:13:54,963 --> 00:13:56,164
It's freezing outside

202
00:13:56,164 --> 00:13:57,424
Quickly sit by the fire

203
00:13:58,122 --> 00:13:59,048
Your Majesty look

204
00:13:59,048 --> 00:14:01,670
Are these plum blossoms I picked for Jiejie pretty?

205
00:14:01,670 --> 00:14:03,393
Your sister was just talking about plum blossoms

206
00:14:03,862 --> 00:14:04,864
and you came.

207
00:14:04,864 --> 00:14:07,671
Of course, I know Jiejie the best

208
00:14:08,538 --> 00:14:11,038
Lingering Chun seems to have grown much taller

209
00:14:11,038 --> 00:14:12,077
Your Majesty, did you forget?

210
00:14:12,077 --> 00:14:14,439
After this year end, I will be 17

211
00:14:15,315 --> 00:14:16,480
Don't just talk

212
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:17,807
Quickly dust off the snow on you

213
00:14:17,807 --> 00:14:20,469
If you catch a cold, don't cry when you have to take medicine!

214
00:14:21,844 --> 00:14:22,942
Still carrying it

215
00:14:22,942 --> 00:14:24,227
Have it put in a vase

216
00:14:24,227 --> 00:14:25,079
Jinxi

217
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:28,122
Jiejie, don't you have a white porcelain vase?

218
00:14:28,122 --> 00:14:30,024
That would be best for the red plum blossoms

219
00:14:31,058 --> 00:14:32,489
You picked some good plum blossoms

220
00:14:32,489 --> 00:14:33,836
They're still buds

221
00:14:33,836 --> 00:14:35,301
and will bloom for a while.

222
00:14:35,669 --> 00:14:37,148
I just love that color

223
00:14:37,148 --> 00:14:38,363
Makes the heart warm inside

224
00:14:40,154 --> 00:14:41,835
I did this for Jiejie

225
00:14:41,835 --> 00:14:43,277
What will you reward me with?

226
00:14:45,144 --> 00:14:46,226
I don't have much else

227
00:14:46,226 --> 00:14:48,472
Try some cakes the kitchen just made

228
00:14:48,472 --> 00:14:50,229
Great! Nothing would be better.

229
00:14:51,277 --> 00:14:52,790
Thanks to you,

230
00:14:53,353 --> 00:14:55,554
I also get to eat something.

231
00:14:55,554 --> 00:15:00,157
If you didn't come, your sister would starve me

232
00:15:00,157 --> 00:15:01,427
My sister wouldn't!

233
00:15:01,667 --> 00:15:03,686
My sister loves Your Majesty the most

234
00:15:04,047 --> 00:15:06,778
If sister means to starve your majesty

235
00:15:06,778 --> 00:15:08,432
it must be your majesty was staring at sister

236
00:15:08,432 --> 00:15:10,008
and has no time to eat

237
00:15:10,008 --> 00:15:13,581
Listen, what a sharp tongue. She must have learned that from you.

238
00:15:13,581 --> 00:15:16,117
Keep eating. Even eating can't stop you from talking.

239
00:15:17,330 --> 00:15:19,994
Today, I'm not the emperor

240
00:15:20,503 --> 00:15:24,421
I will just pretend I'm the young master of a common noble family

241
00:15:24,758 --> 00:15:26,892
Can't I be a little talkative?

242
00:15:26,892 --> 00:15:28,357
I dare not order Your Majesty around

243
00:15:29,025 --> 00:15:31,436
but I dare order a common young master around.

244
00:15:32,494 --> 00:15:34,191
If you don't finish copying these verses,

245
00:15:34,722 --> 00:15:36,464
don't think about dinner tonight!

246
00:15:37,825 --> 00:15:40,542
Listen, isn't your sister overbearing?

247
00:15:40,542 --> 00:15:43,741
She's my sister! Of course I don't think she's overbearing!

248
00:15:45,488 --> 00:15:48,766
You grind the ink. If you don't, I won't write.

249
00:16:05,663 --> 00:16:07,523
Originally I couldn't figure out

250
00:16:07,523 --> 00:16:11,006
why the two of you together looked so familiar to me.

251
00:16:11,006 --> 00:16:12,434
My own sister

252
00:16:12,434 --> 00:16:14,754
and brother-in-law back home are also this way.

253
00:16:14,754 --> 00:16:16,703
One grinds the ink, the other writes

254
00:16:16,703 --> 00:16:17,926
You ate too much

255
00:16:17,926 --> 00:16:19,372
Quickly, drink some water to wash it down

256
00:16:19,372 --> 00:16:21,494
Why won't you let her finish?

257
00:16:22,892 --> 00:16:24,346
Keep talking

258
00:16:24,346 --> 00:16:26,407
Your majesty just likes listening to the nonsenses

259
00:16:27,216 --> 00:16:29,827
Before, when my sister and brother-in-law were together,

260
00:16:29,827 --> 00:16:32,038
they were very close despite not saying much.

261
00:16:32,677 --> 00:16:34,873
My mother calls this...

262
00:16:35,432 --> 00:16:36,663
calls this...

263
00:16:37,805 --> 00:16:39,841
she calls it the joy of the lady's chamber!

264
00:16:41,131 --> 00:16:43,798
Chun'er is still young, where did you hear such things?

265
00:16:43,798 --> 00:16:45,305
It's nonsense

266
00:16:45,904 --> 00:16:47,693
And Your Majesty indulges her!

267
00:16:47,693 --> 00:16:50,632
Your Majesty, do you think I'm speaking nonsense?

268
00:16:50,632 --> 00:16:52,222
Of course not

269
00:16:52,222 --> 00:16:54,604
What you said was excellent

270
00:16:55,849 --> 00:16:58,593
Huan Huan and I are like that

271
00:17:06,219 --> 00:17:07,684
Young mistress

272
