00:30:46,868 --> 00:30:49,372
I thought you were smart and perceptive

539
00:30:49,372 --> 00:30:51,287
I never knew you could be so stupid

540
00:30:51,287 --> 00:30:54,186
How dare you cast a curse in the palace?

541
00:30:54,186 --> 00:30:56,982
I was ignorant, please forgive me

542
00:30:56,982 --> 00:30:59,807
You're not just ignorant but also impossibly stupid

543
00:30:59,807 --> 00:31:01,295
If Princess of Glory saw this,

544
00:31:01,295 --> 00:31:02,898
do you still want to live?

545
00:31:04,467 --> 00:31:08,124
These curses rely on the spirits

546
00:31:08,124 --> 00:31:11,307
but your luck and life is only in your hands

547
00:31:11,307 --> 00:31:13,687
If curses really worked,

548
00:31:13,687 --> 00:31:16,597
no one will need to use their brain to think!

549
00:31:17,313 --> 00:31:18,853
I was stupid

550
00:31:21,527 --> 00:31:24,842
I don't care how much you hate Princess of Glory

551
00:31:24,842 --> 00:31:26,534
I just want to tell you

552
00:31:27,273 --> 00:31:29,482
instead of wasting your time on curses

553
00:31:29,482 --> 00:31:33,332
you should spend you time on the Emperor <br><br> it's half the work, twice the effect

554
00:31:34,171 --> 00:31:35,593
I was wrong

555
00:31:38,793 --> 00:31:40,162
You stupid girl

556
00:31:42,850 --> 00:31:46,274
Burn it. I didn't see anything

557
00:31:46,274 --> 00:31:49,189
I am grateful to Niang Niang

558
00:31:50,816 --> 00:31:53,882
You're alone in the palace, it's inevitable to feel desolate

559
00:31:56,356 --> 00:31:58,819
Even if you have a sister like Precious Smile

560
00:31:59,356 --> 00:32:01,058
but she is deep in the Emperor's favor

561
00:32:01,058 --> 00:32:03,533
I'm afraid she can't think about you all the time

562
00:32:03,533 --> 00:32:05,086
If you have any more grievance in the future

563
00:32:05,086 --> 00:32:06,536
tell it to me

564
00:32:07,226 --> 00:32:10,835
You musn't have stupid thoughts again

565
00:32:10,835 --> 00:32:12,491
Niang Niang's concern for me

566
00:32:13,150 --> 00:32:16,980
I will bring it to heart and never forget

567
00:32:16,980 --> 00:32:19,788
Good, get up. It's cold on the floor

568
00:32:24,290 --> 00:32:27,868
Luckily someone told me about this

569
00:32:27,868 --> 00:32:29,648
I'll never have known otherwise

570
00:32:29,648 --> 00:32:31,197
May I be bold

571
00:32:31,767 --> 00:32:34,547
and ask Niang Niang who it was

572
00:32:35,124 --> 00:32:37,548
Of course it was your close sister

573
00:32:38,173 --> 00:32:39,994
but she didn't mean to

574
00:32:39,994 --> 00:32:41,413
She had no choice

575
00:32:42,365 --> 00:32:44,439
I told her already

576
00:32:45,036 --> 00:32:47,828
this incident

577
00:32:47,828 --> 00:32:49,552
ends with me

578
00:32:49,552 --> 00:32:50,941
Was it Sister Wan?

579
00:32:50,941 --> 00:32:52,764
Don't ask anymore

580
00:32:52,764 --> 00:32:56,445
Just take care of your body and everything else will be fine

581
00:32:59,066 --> 00:33:00,964
I respectful send Niang Niang off

582
00:33:16,464 --> 00:33:18,292
Young mistress, it's time for your medicine

583
00:33:23,574 --> 00:33:24,853
Young mistress?

584
00:33:30,463 --> 00:33:31,443
Young mistress!

585
00:33:31,443 --> 00:33:33,515
How dare you bite the hand that feeds you!

586
00:33:33,515 --> 00:33:35,598
I don't know what I did wrong

587
00:33:35,598 --> 00:33:37,698
but please punish me!

588
00:33:38,457 --> 00:33:40,575
But I dare not

589
00:33:40,575 --> 00:33:42,747
bite the hand that feeds me

590
00:33:42,747 --> 00:33:45,137
You're always the one who cleans my chamber

591
00:33:45,137 --> 00:33:47,737
you know exactly what is in my palace

592
00:33:47,737 --> 00:33:49,798
How dare you say you don't know?

593
00:33:49,798 --> 00:33:51,580
Young mistress, please calm down

594
00:33:51,580 --> 00:33:54,210
I do clean young mistress' chamber

595
00:33:54,210 --> 00:33:57,511
but recently you won't let me touch your bed

596
00:33:57,511 --> 00:33:59,526
I don't know if something went missing or what

597
00:33:59,526 --> 00:34:01,119
but I really don't know!

598
00:34:01,816 --> 00:34:05,286
Then again, I'm not the only one who's allowed in this chamber

599
00:34:05,286 --> 00:34:06,867
There's also Ju Qing

600
00:34:06,867 --> 00:34:08,664
If something really went missing

601
00:34:08,664 --> 00:34:10,935
I'm not the only suspect!

602
00:34:10,935 --> 00:34:12,226
Ju Qing

603
00:34:12,226 --> 00:34:13,537
Yes

604
00:34:13,537 --> 00:34:17,309
Few days ago, young mistress said it's cold and wanted a thicker blanket

605
00:34:17,984 --> 00:34:20,328
It was Ju Qing who did it

606
00:34:21,451 --> 00:34:23,782
Luckily I remembered your order

607
00:34:23,782 --> 00:34:25,521
and told her to just leave it there

608
00:34:25,521 --> 00:34:28,337
No one is allowed to touch young mistress's bed

609
00:34:28,337 --> 00:34:30,315
Yes,

610
00:34:31,798 --> 00:34:33,366
there's also Ju Qing

611
00:34:34,793 --> 00:34:38,398
She was originally Sister's servant

612
00:34:40,623 --> 00:34:43,698
Bao Juan, get up quickly, let me see your injury

613
00:34:43,698 --> 00:34:45,060
I dare not

614
00:34:46,070 --> 00:34:49,319
It's all my fault, I was too harsh

615
00:34:50,094 --> 00:34:53,563
But Bao Juan, you are my trusted aide

616
00:34:53,563 --> 00:34:55,268
that's why I was so harsh

617
00:34:56,183 --> 00:35:00,820
I was afraid you were the one who disclosed my information to others

618
00:35:00,820 --> 00:35:04,221
Young mistress, I wouldn't dare

619
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:08,598
I hoped it wasn't you

620
00:35:10,774 --> 00:35:12,811
but I never thought it would be Ju Qing

621
00:35:12,811 --> 00:35:16,011
Young mistress, you suspect Ju Qing?

622
00:35:16,011 --> 00:35:18,129
She was originally Sister's servant

623
00:35:18,742 --> 00:35:21,740
Aside from her, there's no one else

624
00:35:23,754 --> 00:35:27,178
I thought Sister was doing me a favor

625
00:35:27,178 --> 00:35:29,098
by sending her to serve me

626
00:35:30,376 --> 00:35:34,678
I never thought she wanted to plant a mole

627
00:35:35,450 --> 00:35:36,893
right under my eye

628
00:35:42,231 --> 00:35:43,434
I remember Internal Affairs Authority

629
00:35:43,434 --> 00:35:45,095
sent over two otter fur garments

630
00:35:45,751 --> 00:35:47,655
Remember to give them to Pin of Respects

631
00:35:47,655 --> 00:35:49,058
one for her

632
00:35:49,058 --> 00:35:51,962
and ask her to secretly give the other to Sister Mei

633
00:35:51,962 --> 00:35:52,884
I know

634
00:35:54,086 --> 00:35:56,033
I originally thought with Pin of Respects as the supervisor

635
00:35:56,033 --> 00:35:57,853
I could still go see Sister Mei sometimes

636
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:59,895
But with Princess of Glory watching so closely

637
00:35:59,895 --> 00:36:01,552
there's no loophole at all

638
00:36:02,755 --> 00:36:04,028
Young mistress, don't worry

639
00:36:04,028 --> 00:36:06,066
Wait until the year passes and spring comes

640
00:36:06,066 --> 00:36:08,136
find a time when His Majesty is happy

641
00:36:08,136 --> 00:36:10,033
and try to persuade him to release Mistress Mei

642
00:36:11,578 --> 00:36:13,457
Also remember to urge them back home,

643
00:36:13,457 --> 00:36:14,894
they must catch Liu Ben

644
00:36:14,894 --> 00:36:16,197
Yes

645
00:36:16,197 --> 00:36:17,295
Young mistress, let's hurry

646
00:36:17,295 --> 00:36:18,808
I heard the Empress Dowager will be there too

647
00:36:18,808 --> 00:36:20,492
even the 17th prince is back

648
00:36:20,492 --> 00:36:22,255
It will be bad if we're late

649
00:36:22,255 --> 00:36:23,384
Let's go

650
00:36:24,053 --> 00:36:26,845
This time I went to the old plank roads of Jiange County and Zitong County,

651
00:36:26,845 --> 00:36:28,310
Li Bing's Dujiangyan,

652
00:36:28,310 --> 00:36:30,379
and Du Fu's residence in Huanhua

653
00:36:31,384 --> 00:36:33,363
Did you see the Thousand Buddha Rock?

654
00:36:33,363 --> 00:36:35,465
I know Imperial Mother care about the Buddhas,

655
00:36:35,465 --> 00:36:37,323
so I prayed to each of them for Imperial Mother

656
00:36:38,191 --> 00:36:40,109
You have quite the filial piety

657
00:36:40,868 --> 00:36:43,733
The Shu Road is harder to climb than the sky

658
00:36:43,733 --> 00:36:45,524
This has been a difficult trip

659
00:36:49,411 --> 00:36:51,524
Princess of Glory, this is a nice outfit

660
00:36:51,945 --> 00:36:53,890
Although I have bad eyesights,

661
00:36:54,373 --> 00:36:56,676
it still dazzles my eyes

662
00:36:59,187 --> 00:37:00,903
Empress Dowager gave me that hair ornament

663
00:37:00,903 --> 00:37:04,297
and I thought I should have some nice clothes <br><br> to compliment it

664
00:37:04,684 --> 00:37:07,662
So I had the Embroidery House made me some

665
00:37:07,662 --> 00:37:10,194
The clothes must match the accessories

666
00:37:10,194 --> 00:37:13,537
the silk flowers you wear

667
00:37:13,537 --> 00:37:15,518
must have costed a fortune too

668
00:37:15,518 --> 00:37:18,768
The silk flowers given in the palace are all made of satin

669
00:37:18,768 --> 00:37:21,627
They are pretty but also rot easily

670
00:37:21,627 --> 00:37:24,341
The ones I use are embroided with gold threads

671
00:37:24,341 --> 00:37:27,063
and connected with gemstone beads

672
00:37:27,063 --> 00:37:30,830
They are pretty, but they must cost a lot too?

673
00:37:32,731 --> 00:37:34,630
Thank Empress for the concern,

674
00:37:34,630 --> 00:37:37,063
but I have subsidies from home

675
00:37:37,063 --> 00:37:38,801
I don't have to waste the palace's money

676
00:37:40,538 --> 00:37:44,189
It'll be nice if we all had a family like Princess of Glory

677
00:37:44,189 --> 00:37:46,211
then we won't have to wait on the monthly allowances

678
00:37:46,211 --> 00:37:47,937
and live so stingily

679
00:37:50,176 --> 00:37:52,144
Even if I have a good family

680
00:37:52,144 --> 00:37:54,613
it's because of His Majesty's appreciation

681
00:37:54,613 --> 00:37:56,729
Nian Genyao only has one sister

682
00:37:56,729 --> 00:37:58,897
of course he subsidizes you with

683
00:37:58,897 --> 00:38:00,436
everything I gave him

684
00:38:03,364 --> 00:38:06,328
Empress Dowager, it's time for your medicine

685
00:38:06,328 --> 00:38:08,367
The Imperial Doctor is waiting in the palace

686
00:38:09,304 --> 00:38:10,461
Emperor,

687
00:38:10,461 --> 00:38:13,651
I don't feel well, I will leave now

688
00:38:13,651 --> 00:38:15,520
Imperial Mother must take care of yourself

689
00:38:15,520 --> 00:38:17,049
so I will not worry

690
00:38:23,631 --> 00:38:25,992
Respectfully sends Empress Dowager off

691
00:38:29,873 --> 00:38:32,256
This is the wine made by Precious Smile

692
00:38:32,256 --> 00:38:33,720
everyone have a taste

693
00:38:34,476 --> 00:38:36,284
This is osmanthus flower wine

694
00:38:38,878 --> 00:38:41,105
Precious Smile and I picked the freshely opened osmanthus

695
00:38:41,105 --> 00:38:44,437
from this autumn to make this wine

696
00:38:45,403 --> 00:38:47,196
That's why Imperial Brother is so pleased

697
00:38:47,196 --> 00:38:48,902
and wanted us to treat it

698
00:38:49,696 --> 00:38:52,924
In a family feast, with all the princes,

699
00:38:52,924 --> 00:38:56,289
the osmanthus wine is sweet but also slightly meager

700
00:38:57,098 --> 00:38:59,797
If we treat the guests with fine wines from the palace

701
00:38:59,797 --> 00:39:01,584
wouldn't it demonstrate the style of the Imperial family better?

702
00:39:02,558 --> 00:39:04,242
The war in the northwest just ended

703
00:39:04,242 --> 00:39:06,480
even the Empress Dowager and the Emperor are cutting expenses

704
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:09,004
of course the inner palace has to follow suit

705
00:39:09,890 --> 00:39:11,818
Replacing the expensive wines

706
00:39:11,818 --> 00:39:14,469
with the osmanthus wine personally made by the Emperor,

707
00:39:14,469 --> 00:39:17,068
it not only shows the intention of cutting expenses

708
00:39:17,068 --> 00:39:19,171
but also shows the closeness of the Imperial family

709
00:39:20,211 --> 00:39:23,770
It's good that Precious Smile wants to cut down expenses

710
00:39:23,770 --> 00:39:27,395
but I heard <br><br> Precious has a pair of jade shoes made with Shu silk

711
00:39:27,395 --> 00:39:28,810
the luxury can not be matched

712
00:39:28,810 --> 00:39:32,287
I don't know if I can see them sometimes?

713
00:39:34,146 --> 00:39:37,135
His Majesty gave them to Sister Wan because he likes her!

714
00:39:37,135 --> 00:39:39,807
Of course it should be as luxurious as possible!

715
00:39:39,807 --> 00:39:42,419
If His Majesty wants to, why not?

716
00:39:42,419 --> 00:39:43,964
Isn't that right, Your Majesty?

717
00:39:45,811 --> 00:39:49,370
You always say what's on your mind, that's the thing I like the most about you

718
00:39:51,141 --> 00:39:53,781
Precious Fucha, don't you think so?

